To compile you will need the following tools:
Essential:
	build-essential
	autoconf
	libtool
Libraries:
	libtinyxml2-dev

If documentation is needed:
	doxygen
	dot (for diagrams)

Plugin Specific:
	for LCDProc you will need the LCDProc package.

Prepare tools:
	./autogen.sh
	./configure CXXFLAGS='-g0 -O3'

then compile with:
	make

For more information please visit the LCDSpicer 2 website http://lcdspicer.medutech.net
